  "sections": [
    {
      "reading_order": 1,
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "level": 1,
          "text": "2021-2023 Geographic Information Coordination Council Goals and Strategic Direction",
          "reading_order": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Goal 1. Improve, expand, and support statewide geospatial data and applications.",
          "reading_order": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "table",
          "rows": [
            {
              "is_header_row": true,
              "cells": [
                {
                  "cell_type": "header",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "1.1. Promote free and open discovery of and access to geospatial data created and maintained by local governments."
                    }
                  ],
                  "colspan": 1,
                  "rowspan": 1
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "is_header_row": false,
              "cells": [
                {
                  "cell_type": "data",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Access to local government datasets"
                    }
                  ],
                  "colspan": 1,
                  "rowspan": 1
                },
                {
                  "cell_type": "data",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "LGC – promote value of data"
                    }
                  ],
                  "colspan": 1,
                  "rowspan": 1
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "is_header_row": false,
              "cells": [
                {
                  "cell_type": "data",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "1.2. Research solutions that maintain data sharing security to aid discovery and ease of access to geospatial data."
                    }
                  ],
                  "colspan": 1,
                  "rowspan": 1
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "is_header_row": false,
              "cells": [
                {
                  "cell_type": "data",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Local data access constrained by security policy"
                    }
                  ],
                  "colspan": 1,
                  "rowspan": 1
                },
                {
                  "cell_type": "data",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "TAC - clarify policies, needs, risks, alternatives."
                    }
                  ],
                  "colspan": 1,
                  "rowspan": 1
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "is_header_row": false,
              "cells": [
                {
                  "cell_type": "data",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "1.3. Continue to support initiatives that compile and maintain statewide geospatial datasets that benefit the businesses and citizens of North Carolina."
                    }
                  ],
                  "colspan": 1,
                  "rowspan": 1
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "is_header_row": false,
              "cells": [
                {
                  "cell_type": "data",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Data sharing local to state"
                    }
                  ],
                  "colspan": 1,
                  "rowspan": 1
                },
                {
                  "cell_type": "data",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "SMAC- Prioritize streams and municipal boundaries"
                    }
                  ],
                  "colspan": 1,
                  "rowspan": 1
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "is_header_row": false,
              "cells": [
                {
                  "cell_type": "data",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "1.4. Find solutions to make data sharing local-to-state more efficient to meet the needs of multiple statewide datasets and not place undue burden on local geospatial data managers."
                    }
                  ],
                  "colspan": 1,
                  "rowspan": 1
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "is_header_row": false,
              "cells": [
                {
                  "cell_type": "data",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Data sharing local to state"
                    }
                  ],
                  "colspan": 1,
                  "rowspan": 1
                },
                {
                  "cell_type": "data",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "SGUC – define technical and policy solutions"
                    }
                  ],
                  "colspan": 1,
                  "rowspan": 1
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "is_header_row": false,
              "cells": [
                {
                  "cell_type": "data",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "1.5. Request all state agencies to make the Council’s priority geospatial datasets discoverable and accessible through the NC OneMap Geospatial Portal."
                    }
                  ],
                  "colspan": 1,
                  "rowspan": 1
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "is_header_row": false,
              "cells": [
                {
                  "cell_type": "data",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Priority data accessible via NC OneMap"
                    }
                  ],
                  "colspan": 1,
                  "rowspan": 1
                },
                {
                  "cell_type": "data",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "SGUC – define technical and policy solutions"
                    }
                  ],
                  "colspan": 1,
                  "rowspan": 1
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "is_header_row": false,
              "cells": [
                {
                  "cell_type": "data",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "1.6. Promote geospatial metadata for standard documentation."
                    }
                  ],
                  "colspan": 1,
                  "rowspan": 1
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "is_header_row": false,
              "cells": [
                {
                  "cell_type": "data",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Geospatial metadata"
                    }
                  ],
                  "colspan": 1,
                  "rowspan": 1
                },
                {
                  "cell_type": "data",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "SMAC – metadata training and implementation"
                    }
                  ],
                  "colspan": 1,
                  "rowspan": 1
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "is_header_row": false,
              "cells": [
                {
                  "cell_type": "data",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "1.7. Support applications that derive business value from geospatial data assets and analytics."
                    }
                  ],
                  "colspan": 1,
                  "rowspan": 1
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "is_header_row": false,
              "cells": [
                {
                  "cell_type": "data",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Geospatial Services – geocoding, routing, modeling"
                    }
                  ],
                  "colspan": 1,
                  "rowspan": 1
                },
                {
                  "cell_type": "data",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "SMAC – Requirements and benefits\nLGC – Promote sharing of source data for roads and address points"
                    }
                  ],
                  "colspan": 1,
                  "rowspan": 1
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "is_header_row": false,
              "cells": [
                {
                  "cell_type": "data",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Other applications – from data assets and analytics"
                    }
                  ],
                  "colspan": 1,
                  "rowspan": 1
                },
                {
                  "cell_type": "data",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "SGUC – identify common opportunities and requirements.\nLGC – identify common opportunities and requirements."
                    }
                  ],
                  "colspan": 1,
                  "rowspan": 1
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "reading_order": 3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "reading_order": 2,
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Goal 2. Collaborate and conduct outreach for more integration of geospatial data in information technology for expanded benefits in the geospatial community in North Carolina."
            }
          ],
          "reading_order": 4
        },
        {
          "type": "table",
          "rows": [
            {
              "is_header_row": true,
              "cells": [
                {
                  "cell_type": "header",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "2.1. Identify opportunities to collaborate on GIS solutions in state departments and divisions not directly represented on the Council to add value to state business processes."
                    }
                  ],
                  "colspan": 1,
                  "rowspan": 1
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "is_header_row": false,
              "cells": [
                {
                  "cell_type": "data",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Collaborate with non-GICC State agencies to add value."
                    }
                  ],
                  "colspan": 1,
                  "rowspan": 1
                },
                {
                  "cell_type": "data",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "SGUC – Identify needs and opportunities; optimize GIS and IT resources."
                    }
                  ],
                  "colspan": 1,
                  "rowspan": 1
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "is_header_row": false,
              "cells": [
                {
                  "cell_type": "data",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "2.2. Identify opportunities to collaborate on geospatial data and technical solutions on a regional basis, engaging councils of government, educational institutions, metropolitan planning organizations, and rural planning organizations."
                    }
                  ],
                  "colspan": 1,
                  "rowspan": 1
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "is_header_row": false,
              "cells": [
                {
                  "cell_type": "data",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Collaborate on a regional basis, engaging councils of government."
                    }
                  ],
                  "colspan": 1,
                  "rowspan": 1
                },
                {
                  "cell_type": "data",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "LGC – identify opportunities in working groups"
                    }
                  ],
                  "colspan": 1,
                  "rowspan": 1
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "is_header_row": false,
              "cells": [
                {
                  "cell_type": "data",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "2.3. Reach out to jurisdictions with the least resources to find ways to add value with geospatial data and applications."
                    }
                  ],
                  "colspan": 1,
                  "rowspan": 1
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "is_header_row": false,
              "cells": [
                {
                  "cell_type": "data",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Reach out to local governments with the least resources"
                    }
                  ],
                  "colspan": 1,
                  "rowspan": 1
                },
                {
                  "cell_type": "data",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "LGC – identify needs and practical ways to assist\nSMAC – assist in technical support"
                    }
                  ],
                  "colspan": 1,
                  "rowspan": 1
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "is_header_row": false,
              "cells": [
                {
                  "cell_type": "data",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "2.4. Increase awareness and adoption of Council initiatives and priorities through outreach and education"
                    }
                  ],
                  "colspan": 1,
                  "rowspan": 1
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "is_header_row": false,
              "cells": [
                {
                  "cell_type": "data",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Engage the GIS community at the local, state, and federal level to promote initiatives"
                    }
                  ],
                  "colspan": 1,
                  "rowspan": 1
                },
                {
                  "cell_type": "data",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "LGC, SGUC, FIC – Share opportunities for collaboration, promote initiatives, promote the value of GIS"
                    }
                  ],
                  "colspan": 1,
                  "rowspan": 1
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "reading_order": 5
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "footnotes": []
}